               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1399" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1399" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1399" type="surname" value="THORNTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1399" type="given" value="FREDERICK"></interp>FREDERICK THORNTON</persName>
                  </hi>. I was at Greenwich fair, with my brother—on the 20th of May, at half-past nine o'clock at night, I saw the prisoner</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183906170269"></xptr>
               <p>pull up two or three gentlemen's pockets—he took this handkerchief from one gentleman's pocket, and put it under his frock—I said, "What are you about?"—he said, "Nothing"—I took it from him, and gave it to my brother—I do not know the gentleman's name.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18390617-name-1400" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1400" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1400" type="surname" value="THORNTON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18390617-name-1400" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE THORNTON</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 109.) I am the brother of the last witness—he took this handkerchief from the prisoner, and gave it to me—I said to the gentleman, "Is this your handkerchief?"—he said, "Yes"—I told him to come with me—he said he would not—the prisoner cried, and begged to be forgiven, and a lady who was with the gentleman said, "Don't go against him"—I found on the prisoner another handker<lb></lb>chief and a pair of gloves.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence</hi> I was near a show—this witness came and took the handkerchief from under my smock-frock—I do not know How it came there.</p>
